{"type":"message","id":"bde21016","parentId":"d5351ea2","timestamp":"2026-03-10T00:00:52.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，找到了 12 个最近 6 小时内的日志文件。现在我需要分析这些文件中的内容，查找：\n1. 错误和警告\n2. timeout\n3. API 失败\n4. 资源异常\n\n让我先读取这些文件的内容并进行分析。我会使用 grep 和其他工具来提取关键信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_862bcd5c82964c1294b7b174","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/analyze_logs.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n\necho \"=== 错误统计 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 -exec cat {} \\; | \\\n  grep -iE '\"error\"|\"failed\"|\"timeout\"|\"exception\"|\"warning\"' | \\\n  head -100\n\necho -e \"\\n=== API 错误统计 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 -exec cat {} \\; | \\\n  grep -iE '\"status\":[45][0-9]{2}|401|403|429|500|502|503|504' | \\\n  head -50\n\necho -e \"\\n=== 工具调用失败 ===\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 -exec cat {} \\; | \\\n  grep -iE '\"isError\":\\s*true|\"success\":\\s*false' | \\\n  head -50\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/analyze_logs.sh\n/tmp/analyze_logs.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":953,"output":353,"cacheRead":11840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":13146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773100839330}}
