{"type":"message","id":"e3484dde","parentId":"b26b6b0c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T04:01:19.029Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！对比上次分析（08:00）和这次分析（12:00），我看到了显著的改善：\n\n上次分析（02:00-08:00）：\n- Model Context Window 超限：76 次\n- 429 速率限制错误：70 次\n- ENOENT 错误：104 次\n- 超时错误：150 次\n- 子代理失败：9 次\n\n这次分析（06:00-12:00）：\n- Model Context Window 超限：13 次（↓ 83%）\n- 429 速率限制错误：69 次（↓ 1%，几乎持平）\n- ENOENT 错误：38 次（↓ 63%）\n- 超时错误：82 次（↓ 45%）\n- 子代理失败：16 次（↑ 78%，增加！）\n\n看起来 MEMORY.md 精炼效果显著（Context Window 超限减少 83%），但是子代理失败率反而增加了。让我深入分析子代理失败的原因。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_1318c9c24bcf49dfa7b62b60","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/subagent_analysis.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n\necho \"=== 子代理失败分析 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"## 失败的子代理详情\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -A 5 '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep -E '\"label\"|\"errorMessage\"|\"runtimeMs\"' | head -50\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 失败原因统计\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -B 10 '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep '\"errorMessage\"' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 成功的子代理数量\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep '\"status\":\"done\"' | grep -E '\"label\":\"小说评审' | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 失败的子代理数量\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep -E '\"label\":\"小说评审' | wc -l\n\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/subagent_analysis.sh\n/tmp/subagent_analysis.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1339,"output":582,"cacheRead":113664,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":115585,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"