. **紧急报告**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/urgent-stagger-config-not-applied-20260310-1203.md` (2.5 KB)\n4. **Evolution History**: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds/round-295-20260310-1200.md` (1.9 KB)\n5. **Pattern Registry**: 已更新（新增 PAT-063，更新 PAT-060/061/062）\n\n---\n\n## 📝 结论\n\n### 主要成就\n1. ✅ **MEMORY.md 精炼效果显著**（Context Window 超限 ↓83%）\n2. ✅ **系统稳定性显著提升**（ENOENT ↓63%，超时 ↓45%）\n\n### 主要问题\n1. 🔴 **子代理串行化配置未生效**（需要立即应用）\n2. 🔴 **子代理失败率恶化**（42% → 53%）\n3. 🔴 **Aborted 错误新增**（23 次）\n\n### 关键发现\n- **MEMORY.md 精炼是正确的方向**，应该继续维护\n- **子代理串行化需要立即应用**，当前配置未生效\n- **需要更积极的措施**来减少 429 错误和子代理失败\n\n---\n\n**下次分析**: 2026-03-10 18:00\n**重点验证**: 子代理串行化配置是否生效，429 错误是否减少"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1371,"output":1217,"cacheRead":68544,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":71132,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773115567295}}
