{"type":"message","id":"20794ded","parentId":"17a26e2e","timestamp":"2026-03-10T08:01:36.015Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个结果很有意思：\n\n1. **429 速率限制错误**: 101 次（上次 69 次，增加了 32 次，↑ 46%）\n2. **Context Window 超限**: 19 次（上次 13 次，增加了 6 次，↑ 46%）\n3. **子代理失败率**: 20 失败 / 25 成功 = 44%（上次 53%，改善了 9%）\n4. **ENOENT 错误**: 50 次（上次 38 次，增加了 12 次，↑ 32%）\n5. **超时错误**: 104 次（上次 82 次，增加了 22 次，↑ 27%）\n6. **Aborted 错误**: 42 次（上次 23 次，增加了 19 次，↑ 83%）\n\n看起来系统状态在恶化，而不是改善。429 错误反而增加了，说明子代理串行化配置确实没有生效，或者效果不佳。\n\n让我进一步分析子代理失败的原因。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_873f04fe61d14dc78f9b340b","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/subagent_analysis_v3.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n\necho \"=== 子代理失败分析 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"## 失败的子代理详情（最近 10 个）\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -A 2 '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep -E '\"label\"|\"errorMessage\"' | head -40\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 失败原因统计\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -B 5 '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep '\"errorMessage\"' | grep -oE '\"errorMessage\":\"[^\"]*\"' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 成功 vs 失败比例\"\nSUCCESS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 -exec cat {} \\; | grep -c '\"status\":\"done\"')\nFAILED=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 -exec cat {} \\; | grep -c '\"status\":\"failed\"')\nTOTAL=$((SUCCESS + FAILED))\nRATE=$(awk \"BEGIN {printf \\\"%.1f\\\", ($SUCCESS/$TOTAL)*100}\")\necho \"成功: $SUCCESS, 失败: $FAILED, 总数: $TOTAL, 成功率: $RATE%\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 小说评审子代理统计\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -E '\"label\":\"小说评审' | grep -oE '\"status\":\"(done|failed)\"' | sort | uniq -c\n\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/subagent_analysis_v3.sh\n/tmp/subagent_analysis_v3.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1316,"output":686,"cacheRead":71616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73618,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773129661263}}
