{"type":"message","id":"40c3a0ff","parentId":"3ad534df","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:00:53.444Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"当前时间是 20:00（时间戳 1773144018），最近 6 小时是 14:00-20:00。\n\n我看到有 9 个日志文件，其中一些是新的。让我进行深度分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_3c32f55ec9144a96a66cdfe9","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/deep_log_analysis_v4.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n\necho \"=== 深度日志分析（Round 297）===\"\necho \"分析时间: $(date '+%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S')\"\necho \"时间范围: 最近 6 小时（14:00 - 20:00）\"\necho \"\"\n\n# 1. 错误统计\necho \"## 1. 错误类型统计\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -oE '\"errorMessage\":\"[^\"]*\"' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn | head -20\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 2. 429 速率限制错误\"\necho \"总数:\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -i \"429\" | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 3. Model Context Window 错误\"\necho \"总数:\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -i \"model_context_window_exceeded\" | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 4. 子代理状态\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -oE '\"status\":\"(failed|done)\"' | sort | uniq -c\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 5. 工具调用错误\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -oE '\"status\":\"error\"' | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 6. ENOENT 错误\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -i \"ENOENT\" | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 7. 超时错误\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -i \"timeout\\|timed out\" | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 8. Aborted 错误\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -i \"aborted\" | wc -l\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 9. 按时间段统计错误\"\necho \"错误分布（按小时）：\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -E '\"errorMessage\"|\"error\":|\"stopReason\":\"error\"' | grep -oE '\"timestamp\":\"[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}T[0-9]{2}:[0-9]{2}' | \\\n  sed 's/.*T\\([0-9]*\\):.*/\\1/' | sort | uniq -c | sort -k2 -n\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 10. Token 使用统计\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -oE '\"totalTokens\":[0-9]+' | sed 's/.*://' | awk '{sum+=$1; count++} END {print \"总 Token: \" sum \" (平均: \" int(sum/count) \")\"}'\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 11. 新增：子代理启动时间间隔分析\"\necho \"检查是否有延迟启动的效果：\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep -E '\"startedAt\":[0-9]+' | grep -oE '\"startedAt\":[0-9]+' | sed 's/\"startedAt\"://' | awk 'NR>1 {diff=($1-prev)/1000; if(diff>0 && diff<300) print \"间隔: \" diff \" 秒\"; count++} {prev=$1}' | head -10\n\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/deep_log_analysis_v4.sh\n/tmp/deep_log_analysis_v4.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":861,"output":1167,"cacheRead":111616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":113644,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773144018556}}
