{"type":"message","id":"c3dffc9e","parentId":"c6f345cc","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:01:23.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好消息！我看到了一些改进的迹象：\n\n1. **子代理启动间隔增加**：从几乎同时启动，到现在有明显的间隔（21-209秒），这说明可能有某种延迟机制在起作用，虽然还不够激进（我们建议 60 秒）。\n\n2. **但是 429 错误仍然在增加**：从 101 增加到 124（↑23%），说明当前的延迟还不够。\n\n3. **子代理成功率有所改善**：从 37%（11/30）提升到 58%（36/62），这是一个积极的信号。\n\n4. **Context Window 错误增加**：从 19 增加到 24（↑26%），需要关注。\n\n5. **Aborted 错误继续增加**：从 42 增加到 61（↑45%）。\n\n让我进行更详细的分析。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_5086de64409a4926b1030fa8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat > /tmp/subagent_analysis_v4.sh << 'EOF'\n#!/bin/bash\n\necho \"=== 子代理详细分析 ===\"\necho \"\"\n\necho \"## 成功 vs 失败比例\"\nSUCCESS=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 -exec cat {} \\; | grep -c '\"status\":\"done\"')\nFAILED=$(find /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 -exec cat {} \\; | grep -c '\"status\":\"failed\"')\nTOTAL=$((SUCCESS + FAILED))\nRATE=$(awk \"BEGIN {printf \\\"%.1f\\\", ($SUCCESS/$TOTAL)*100}\")\necho \"成功: $SUCCESS, 失败: $FAILED, 总数: $TOTAL, 成功率: $RATE%\"\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 失败原因统计\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -B 5 '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep '\"errorMessage\"' | grep -oE '\"errorMessage\":\"[^\"]*\"' | sort | uniq -c | sort -rn\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 最近失败的子代理（最近 10 个）\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep -A 2 '\"status\":\"failed\"' | grep -E '\"label\"|\"runtimeMs\"' | tail -30\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 子代理启动间隔分析（最近 20 个）\"\nfind /root/.openclaw/agents/main/sessions -name \"*.jsonl\" -type f -mtime -0.25 | while read f; do\n  cat \"$f\"\ndone | grep '\"status\":\"failed\"\\|\"status\":\"done\"' | grep -E '\"startedAt\":[0-9]+' | grep -oE '\"startedAt\":[0-9]+' | sed 's/\"startedAt\"://' | awk 'NR>1 {diff=($1-prev)/1000; print \"间隔: \" diff \" 秒\"} {prev=$1}' | tail -20\n\necho \"\"\necho \"## 与上次对比（成功率）\"\necho \"Round 295 (12:00): 47% (7/15)\"\necho \"Round 296 (16:00): 37% (11/30)\"\necho \"Round 297 (20:00): $RATE% ($SUCCESS/$TOTAL)\"\n\nEOF\nchmod +x /tmp/subagent_analysis_v4.sh\n/tmp/subagent_analysis_v4.sh"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1635,"output":777,"cacheRead":112448,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":114860,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773144053743}}
